{"tid":1391392,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"40L藝術家談大胸女生之苦：胸圍難買　可愛款式只可當情趣內衣","createTime":"2019-07-31T12:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T12:00:53.000Z","uid":81228,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af9d447cecc280ef29dae8352ecef01d102d090e","tid":1391392,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:00:53.000Z","msg":"Viu Tv《對不起，標籤你》第二輯的節目，請來4個「金魚」嘉賓，如南亞裔、地盤工人和露宿，他們當中只有一個人真正是被標籤的一群，而節目中的Tagger成員就要從中猜測誰是真正被標籤的對象。最近播出一集請來「Double May」現身說法，繼續打破標籤。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3070327/org/a268272f29667ef79a37240abee821ad.png/Sc8bz8iDVjMkzhOXSUR-l4pifN4GgNKXWRlV9FkZVfQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3070327%2Forg%2Fa268272f29667ef79a37240abee821ad.png%2FSc8bz8iDVjMkzhOXSUR-l4pifN4GgNKXWRlV9FkZVfQ&h=1a5d2e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3070333/org/f7282b73ae2ec9b037b4d64bab21cec0.png/eygMhvJ55Q4E6fILAdfZzcYMJF3dspfws1Tf1LNU39Q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3070333%2Forg%2Ff7282b73ae2ec9b037b4d64bab21cec0.png%2FeygMhvJ55Q4E6fILAdfZzcYMJF3dspfws1Tf1LNU39Q&h=079658d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3070347/org/139131f0bfad0328738327870142e468.jpg/VO1Aiy33_LuJgFUF2_zg-iSKZsthePdLaGq1JGhqtSQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3070347%2Forg%2F139131f0bfad0328738327870142e468.jpg%2FVO1Aiy33_LuJgFUF2_zg-iSKZsthePdLaGq1JGhqtSQ&h=9a87c226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3070237/org/f882813c171a574fc2144e63d6478ea6.png/iiXaK9rjhpmp7Gi0C64sCzshUco-OQ9g3rQMDd60DA0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3070237%2Forg%2Ff882813c171a574fc2144e63d6478ea6.png%2FiiXaK9rjhpmp7Gi0C64sCzshUco-OQ9g3rQMDd60DA0&h=fea9bd05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3070239/org/ffbe13f028ede95706aceb3cfdb88beb.png/nyV-XYlpVXFAwzVuh2Y8GzcXgqvn_618bQ60Am0OtAI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3070239%2Forg%2Fffbe13f028ede95706aceb3cfdb88beb.png%2FnyV-XYlpVXFAwzVuh2Y8GzcXgqvn_618bQ60Am0OtAI&h=e5efe20f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3070235/org/95a9d1796ef2434c850985ea8ba30a97.png/6IY5GjjCcTiF4G2AZ6cVp5OZvormLv51EJN4khCTeJI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3070235%2Forg%2F95a9d1796ef2434c850985ea8ba30a97.png%2F6IY5GjjCcTiF4G2AZ6cVp5OZvormLv51EJN4khCTeJI&h=2aaba976&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3070233/org/24a2b794df3dfb1ea6c394b353a4d73f.png/JIgRcm6l1ZXiSp83-1oiiEmdLDcLUE_83JkBvtyZAb4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3070233%2Forg%2F24a2b794df3dfb1ea6c394b353a4d73f.png%2FJIgRcm6l1ZXiSp83-1oiiEmdLDcLUE_83JkBvtyZAb4&h=609be156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3070232/org/878e37d8f3800556fd6275bf3bfb1f1d.png/i36cvUM9LFdk_JXkDZqypPbO7nwskOY-71m_4-9Zv-M\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3070232%2Forg%2F878e37d8f3800556fd6275bf3bfb1f1d.png%2Fi36cvUM9LFdk_JXkDZqypPbO7nwskOY-71m_4-9Zv-M&h=3415a0b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3070234/org/6a91289308899a9614d8f37562ca4be8.png/PngVLafz1OGOZJuX15oBmXt4xjsNddcub-FGMm_hRjI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3070234%2Forg%2F6a91289308899a9614d8f37562ca4be8.png%2FPngVLafz1OGOZJuX15oBmXt4xjsNddcub-FGMm_hRjI&h=c6bdd034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3070236/org/50047327b3fda98a01076cf67708433c.png/TL0T_Ltgr4msI2KMBGN9i2IaiKP_g0bn-Txu8_k8bvM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3070236%2Forg%2F50047327b3fda98a01076cf67708433c.png%2FTL0T_Ltgr4msI2KMBGN9i2IaiKP_g0bn-Txu8_k8bvM&h=808b874f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3070240/org/6d741138707f30b4f7271f915dda8f71.png/LqtpDGf_CM6DRNKf1GkavltHrJUNzkUr1n3-XdZ9_l0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3070240%2Forg%2F6d741138707f30b4f7271f915dda8f71.png%2FLqtpDGf_CM6DRNKf1GkavltHrJUNzkUr1n3-XdZ9_l0&h=55eb9246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3070238/org/57a99cfa6d462d933e76231e8494c558.png/9BjRW63eA3p_ckciDZFwguxhfsMkm3j4uSz9Hrks_R4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3070238%2Forg%2F57a99cfa6d462d933e76231e8494c558.png%2F9BjRW63eA3p_ckciDZFwguxhfsMkm3j4uSz9Hrks_R4&h=264d1284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3076200/org/e71789ebf3fa615b90b72851edfa656d.jpg/pV4w-s4g_PTqB8AGLpQ3csznkVtKDRZ8gH067IB9Ouw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3076200%2Forg%2Fe71789ebf3fa615b90b72851edfa656d.jpg%2FpV4w-s4g_PTqB8AGLpQ3csznkVtKDRZ8gH067IB9Ouw&h=e63c2f04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我們總是覺得胸部豐滿的女生很「著數」，總有一堆男生圍着她們轉，向她們獻殷勤；如果她們是「瘦底大波」，就會成為男生眼中的完美女神，仿佛被看待成自帶電力的發電機，衣服隨便穿也能有Sexy感覺，能把男生們迷得神魂顛倒。事實上，大胸女生只想說有苦自己知。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>性感=淫蕩？</strong><br />\n<br />\n身邊不少大胸朋友表示只要穿得稍微性感或緊身，走在街上就會惹來不少目光，猶如被人「視姦」一番。同性的目光更不友善，她們覺得穿着性感的大胸女生一定是另有企圖，心中總是想着「博咩啊？」，如若不幸遭到性侵犯，可能會更容易遭受冷言冷語，他們往往會「Blame the Victim（責怪受害者）」，「唔想被摸就着得密實啲啦」，仿佛身材好就是原罪。更甚是，她們會被貼上不同標籤，節目請來演員陳彥行做嘉賓，因為身材豐滿，往往需要接拍較為性感的角色。她在節目中更坦言過往曾經遭受性騷擾，她會極力澄清「性感不等於淫蕩」。直至後來她成為電台主持，觀眾才開始慢慢認識她的另一面<br />\n<br />\n<strong>大胸=多著數？</strong><br />\n<br />\n而節目中的真「Double May」豐滿女生海諾，創作不少女性主義的作品，她擁有40L的上圍，可能是不少女生夢寐以求的身材，但到底現實是否會較多「著數」？她坦言自己從不會可以向別人討好處，只是好處會自己找上門，可能買切雞飯會送你兩塊紅腸。然而，從鏡子的另一端看，身材好也為她惹來不少猥瑣目光，甚至有些人會得寸進尺，故意撞她的胸部。她分享過往曾經被跟蹤，對方在地鐵中追了她八個月台。除了旁人目光，身材也為她的生活帶來不便，以前曾經試過跳舞，為了更方便而用繃帶束胸。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>這樣的你，其實很美</strong><br />\n<br />\n胸前的兩塊肉，是男生的討論焦點，不論平胸、大胸都取笑一番，為她們取「Ipad」、「人間胸器」等暱稱，但暗地裏女生往往比男生更在意。平胸總是想着如何豐胸，大胸又會想着如何縮胸，我們總是覺得「隔離飯香」，大胸看細胸好，平胸看大胸好，卻忘記了欣賞自己，如同再瘦的女生還是會嚷着要減肥，出門倒垃圾還是要化妝，有時候放開一點，不要總是對着鏡子愁眉苦臉，這樣的你，可能更美。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：周咏詩<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%9F%A5%E6%80%A7%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F/355380/40l%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93%E5%AE%B6%E8%AB%87%E5%A4%A7%E8%83%B8%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E4%B9%8B%E8%8B%A6-%E8%83%B8%E5%9C%8D%E9%9B%A3%E8%B2%B7-%E5%8F%AF%E6%84%9B%E6%AC%BE%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%AA%E5%8F%AF%E7%95%B6%E6%83%85%E8%B6%A3%E5%85%A7%E8%A1%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%2F355380%2F40l%25E8%2597%259D%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25AB%2587%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2583%25B8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B9%258B%25E8%258B%25A6-%25E8%2583%25B8%25E5%259C%258D%25E9%259B%25A3%25E8%25B2%25B7-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%2584%259B%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E5%25BC%258F%25E5%258F%25AA%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%2583%2585%25E8%25B6%25A3%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%25A1%25A3&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=e900af86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%9F%A5%E6%80%A7%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F/355380/40l%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93%E5%AE%B6%E8%AB%87%E5%A4%A7%E8%83%B8%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E4%B9%8B%E8%8B%A6-%E8%83%B8%E5%9C%8D%E9%9B%A3%E8%B2%B7-%E5%8F%AF%E6%84%9B%E6%AC%BE%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%AA%E5%8F%AF%E7%95%B6%E6%83%85%E8%B6%A3%E5%85%A7%E8%A1%A3</a>"}]}